suncertify.db

Interface DatabaseConstants


  • public interface DatabaseConstants
    DatabaseConstants contains information relating to the database schema as outlined in the project specification. Information includes the number of bytes that are used to hold values for different fields and values etc. Design decision- Rather than dynamically creating these values on the fly it is assumed that the database information/schema is not likely to change but if it does this class can be easily updated to refelct this
    Author:
    Kieran O'Brien
